dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Trempealeau County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin in 2021 and includes the layers 'Trempealeau_Hydro_LINE_2021' and 'Trempealeau_Hydro_POLY_2021.' [LINE: Rivers, streams, and creeks. POLY: Lakes]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://co.trempealeau.wi.us/departments/administrative_departments/land_records/data.php
